## All Bugs Fixed (chronological)

| # | Bug | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Ollama sudo install failure | Symlinked binary to `~/.local/bin/ollama` |
| 2 | LLM returning malformed JSON | `_repair_json()`: strip fences, fix commas, Python→JSON literals |
| 3 | LLM hanging on long docs | `LLM_CHAR_BUDGET=4000`, removed `format="json"`, dynamic `num_ctx` |
| 4 | Embed model hanging | Cap embed input to 6000 chars |
| 5 | High RAM after indexing | `unload_models()` called after index complete (`keep_alive=0`) |
| 6 | Electron `require is not defined` | Don't use `"type":"module"` in package.json; keep CommonJS |
| 7 | Nodes piling in center | Strong d3 charge (`-120`), link distance, collide force |
| 8 | Graph flickering every 1.5s | Separate topology from search scores; in-place patching |
| 9 | All labels overlapping | Labels only for hover/selected/top-3 |
| 10 | Scanned PDFs failing silently | Known deferred issue — needs OCR |
| 11 | Inspector card not closing on delete | `loadFullGraph` checks if `selectedNode` still in new graph |
| 12 | Single click not opening card | D3 zoom conflict: replaced with manual pointer events + 4px drag threshold |
| 13 | Deletion node still visible after 5s | `onNodeDeleted` prop calls `loadFullGraph` immediately after `api.deleteFile` |
| 14 | CSP blocked `127.0.0.1` in App.tsx | Use `apiGet()` IPC bridge instead of raw `fetch()` |
| 15 | New files ignored in shared-folder workspace | `add_file_to_workspace` called before `upsert_file` → FK violation; moved to after |
| 16 | Restart mid-indexing lost progress | `_resume_unfinished()` on startup scans for unindexed files |
| 17 | Inspector "Open File" / "Show in Finder" silently broken | Used `node.id` (hash) instead of `node.path` — fixed |

